## ðŸ§© ii. Simulate to Find the Number of Packets Dropped

ðŸŽ¯ *Goal:* Create a situation where some packets are dropped.

*Setup:*

* Scenario Type: *Wired*
* *Nodes:* 3 nodes â†’ n0, n1, n2
* *Links:*

* n0 â†” n1 â†’ Duplex, bandwidth 1 Mb, delay 10 ms
* n1 â†” n2 â†’ Duplex, bandwidth 0.5 Mb (smaller) â†’ *causes drops*
* *Agent:* TCP (on n0) â†’ TCP Sink (on n2)
* *Application:* FTP
* *Simulation time:* 10s
* *Output Files:* drop.tr, drop.nam

âœ… *Expected result:* Some packets get dropped (youâ€™ll later count from drop.tr).

