## ðŸ§  After Running

Run in terminal:

bash
ns filename.tcl


Then:

bash
awk '$1=="d"' filename.tr | wc -l


â†’ gives total drops
or

bash
awk '$1=="d" && tolower($5)=="tcp"' filename.tr | wc -l
awk '$1=="d" && tolower($5)=="cbr"' filename.tr | wc -l


â†’ gives TCP vs UDP drops.
